  m_text: 'The year is 2026. Deep space is under attack by relentless waves of hostile
    alien swarms. As the vanguard of the Starfleet, you control the galaxy''s ultimate
    fighter ship. Your mission is simple: blast through enemy formations, dodge deadly
    kamikaze dives, and claim the ultimate high score!

    But keep your eyes peeled,
    pilot... This sector''s matrix is highly unstable. Rumors speak of hidden system
    glitches and secret <b><color=#0080FF>Easter Eggs</color></b> buried deep within
    the simulation.

    Can you survive the onslaught and uncover the galaxy''s
    greatest secrets?'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
